reviewText: I was not happy as I would have like to see live acts not video. I also wish they had put all the acts that were on the C.D. The dvd was cut to 17 acts,and it was not what I had expected.
It was my third favorite out of WOW Gospel 2008. 2009, and 2010 Video.  The video was inspirational and praises of God can be felt with the presence of God.
Every thing arrived promptly and in great condition. I would recommend this seller to a friend and I would use them again anytime.
I received the product in a timely manner, however it was not what I expected. I thought I was getting video of live performances, and what I got was videos that I could have watched on cable.
I was a little disappointed in the WOW 2009. It used some of the same artist as shown in WOW 2008.
